  "detailed_description": "<strong>--------欢迎来到有史以来最热的幻想乡!交流反馈群号：1025630849--------</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/7db1af61829f4f52cfa2d0e48a8a0b2d.poster.avif?t=1624500369\" width=504 height=746 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/7db1af61829f4f52cfa2d0e48a8a0b2d.webm?t=1624500369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/7db1af61829f4f52cfa2d0e48a8a0b2d.mp4?t=1624500369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概述：</h2><br>本游戏是一款2D横板的东方project二次同人动作RPG游戏，拥有宏大的叙事和独具<br>特色的武器合成/组装系统。玩家将扮演救灾小队穿行于幻想乡各处，探索隐藏的秘<br>宝并调查异变的成因。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/04d4283d3f3d020f87216e4a7cd85b60.poster.avif?t=1624500369\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/04d4283d3f3d020f87216e4a7cd85b60.webm?t=1624500369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/04d4283d3f3d020f87216e4a7cd85b60.mp4?t=1624500369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/170ae9b5a4f1f601bad1a9de4ab1b304.poster.avif?t=1624500369\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/170ae9b5a4f1f601bad1a9de4ab1b304.webm?t=1624500369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/170ae9b5a4f1f601bad1a9de4ab1b304.mp4?t=1624500369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我的化身是什么人：</h2><br>你将操纵由两名异变解决者（一般来说，是灵梦和魔理沙 ） 组成的小队共同作战 ，<br>小队成员拥有各自独特的能力。通过装备搭配，她们能够胜任不同的职能，你随时<br>都可以在两名小队成员之间自由切换。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/4f432fdd3db020b804bed48c595504b2.avif?t=1624500369\" width=504 height=284 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/b19ad6c1568ce9c80a78259f32021dcc.poster.avif?t=1624500369\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/b19ad6c1568ce9c80a78259f32021dcc.webm?t=1624500369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/b19ad6c1568ce9c80a78259f32021dcc.mp4?t=1624500369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >幻想乡发生了什么：</h2><br>由于不明原因，幻想乡的天空出现了十个太阳。这些太阳或是交替出现，或是一同<br>出现，这使得幻想乡笼罩在了似乎永不消散的极昼之中在某些地区，过于强大的太<br>阳热力更是让土壤开裂、房屋燃烧，大量民众不得不躲入地下……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571140/extras/afea61734b4cdbfe2c0e1b54f591b258.avif?t=1624500369\" width=504 height=746 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我应该干什么：</h2><br>作为维系幻想乡平衡的英推，你们的工作自然是解决异变。这次异变的直接体现就<br>是狂暴的太阳，说到太阳的话................最可疑的自然就是地灵殿下方的那位“人工太<br>阳”小姐了吧，虽然这种声势的异变不像是她能做得出来的，但是有错杀没放过，总<br>之先去把她打一顿吧！",
